{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 1", "sort_key": "0001", "text_original": "諸侯行而死於館，則其復如於其國。如於道，則升其乘車之左轂，以其綏復。其輤有裧，緇布裳帷素錦以為屋而行。至於廟門，不毀墻遂入適所殯，唯輤為說於廟門外。", "text_normalized": "諸侯行而死於館，則其復如於其國。如於道，則升其乘車之左轂，以其綏復。其輤有裧，緇布裳帷素錦以為屋而行。至於廟門，不毀墻遂入適所殯，唯輤為說於廟門外。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 2", "sort_key": "0002", "text_original": "大夫、士死於道，則升其乘車之左轂，以其綏復。如於館死，則其復如於家。大夫以布為輤而行，至於家而說輤，載以輲車，入自門至於阼階下而說車，舉自阼階，升適所殯。士輤，葦席以為屋，蒲席以為裳帷。", "text_normalized": "大夫、士死於道，則升其乘車之左轂，以其綏復。如於館死，則其復如於家。大夫以布為輤而行，至於家而說輤，載以輲車，入自門至於阼階下而說車，舉自阼階，升適所殯。士輤，葦席以為屋，蒲席以為裳帷。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 3", "sort_key": "0003", "text_original": "凡訃於其君，曰：「君之臣某死」；父母、妻、長子，曰：「君之臣某之某死」。君訃於他國之君，曰：「寡君不祿，敢告於執事。」；夫人，曰：「寡小君不祿。」；大子之喪，曰：「寡君之適子某死。」", "text_normalized": "凡訃於其君，曰：「君之臣某死」；父母、妻、長子，曰：「君之臣某之某死」。君訃於他國之君，曰：「寡君不祿，敢告於執事。」；夫人，曰：「寡小君不祿。」；大子之喪，曰：「寡君之適子某死。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 4", "sort_key": "0004", "text_original": "大夫訃於同國：適者，曰：「某不祿」；訃於士，亦曰：「某不祿」；訃於他國之君，曰：「君之外臣寡大夫某死」，訃於適者，曰：「吾子之外私寡大夫某不祿，使某實。」訃於士，亦曰：「吾子之外私寡大夫某不祿，使某實。」士訃於同國大夫，曰：「某死」，訃於士，亦曰：「某死」；訃於他國之君，曰：「君之外臣某死」，訃於大夫，曰：「吾子之外私某死」，訃於士，亦曰：「吾子之外私某死」。", "text_normalized": "大夫訃於同國：適者，曰：「某不祿」；訃於士，亦曰：「某不祿」；訃於他國之君，曰：「君之外臣寡大夫某死」，訃於適者，曰：「吾子之外私寡大夫某不祿，使某實。」訃於士，亦曰：「吾子之外私寡大夫某不祿，使某實。」士訃於同國大夫，曰：「某死」，訃於士，亦曰：「某死」；訃於他國之君，曰：「君之外臣某死」，訃於大夫，曰：「吾子之外私某死」，訃於士，亦曰：「吾子之外私某死」。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 5", "sort_key": "0005", "text_original": "大夫次於公館以終喪，士練而歸。士次於公館，大夫居廬，士居堊室。", "text_normalized": "大夫次於公館以終喪，士練而歸。士次於公館，大夫居廬，士居堊室。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 6", "sort_key": "0006", "text_original": "大夫為其父母兄弟之未為大夫者之喪，服如士服。士為其父母兄弟之為大夫者之喪，服如士服。大夫之適子，服大夫之服。大夫之庶子為大夫，則為其父母服大夫服；其位，與未為大夫者齒。", "text_normalized": "大夫為其父母兄弟之未為大夫者之喪，服如士服。士為其父母兄弟之為大夫者之喪，服如士服。大夫之適子，服大夫之服。大夫之庶子為大夫，則為其父母服大夫服；其位，與未為大夫者齒。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 7", "sort_key": "0007", "text_original": "士之子為大夫，則其父母弗能主也，使其子主之。無子，則為之置後。", "text_normalized": "士之子為大夫，則其父母弗能主也，使其子主之。無子，則為之置後。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 8", "sort_key": "0008", "text_original": "大夫卜宅與葬日，有司麻衣、布衰、布帶，因喪屨，緇布冠不蕤。占者皮弁。如筮，則史練冠長衣以筮。占者朝服。", "text_normalized": "大夫卜宅與葬日，有司麻衣、布衰、布帶，因喪屨，緇布冠不蕤。占者皮弁。如筮，則史練冠長衣以筮。占者朝服。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 9, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 9", "sort_key": "0009", "text_original": "大夫之喪，既薦馬。薦馬者，哭踴，出乃包奠而讀書。", "text_normalized": "大夫之喪，既薦馬。薦馬者，哭踴，出乃包奠而讀書。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 10, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 10", "sort_key": "0010", "text_original": "大夫之喪，大宗人相，小宗人命龜，卜人作龜。", "text_normalized": "大夫之喪，大宗人相，小宗人命龜，卜人作龜。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 11, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 11", "sort_key": "0011", "text_original": "復，諸侯以褒衣冕服，爵弁服，夫人稅衣揄狄，狄稅素沙。內子以鞠衣，褒衣，素沙。下大夫以襢衣，其餘如士。復西上。", "text_normalized": "復，諸侯以褒衣冕服，爵弁服，夫人稅衣揄狄，狄稅素沙。內子以鞠衣，褒衣，素沙。下大夫以襢衣，其餘如士。復西上。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 12, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 12", "sort_key": "0012", "text_original": "大夫不揄絞，屬於池下。", "text_normalized": "大夫不揄絞，屬於池下。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 13, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 13", "sort_key": "0013", "text_original": "大夫附於士，士不附於大夫，附於大夫之昆弟。無昆弟，則從其昭穆。雖王父母在，亦然。", "text_normalized": "大夫附於士，士不附於大夫，附於大夫之昆弟。無昆弟，則從其昭穆。雖王父母在，亦然。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 14, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 14", "sort_key": "0014", "text_original": "婦附於其夫之所附之妃，無妃。則亦從其昭穆之妃。妾附於妾祖姑，無妾祖姑則亦從其昭穆之妾。", "text_normalized": "婦附於其夫之所附之妃，無妃。則亦從其昭穆之妃。妾附於妾祖姑，無妾祖姑則亦從其昭穆之妾。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 15, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 15", "sort_key": "0015", "text_original": "男子附於王父則配；女子附於王母，則不配。公子附於公子。", "text_normalized": "男子附於王父則配；女子附於王母，則不配。公子附於公子。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 16, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 16", "sort_key": "0016", "text_original": "君薨，大子號稱子，待猶君也。", "text_normalized": "君薨，大子號稱子，待猶君也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 17, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 17", "sort_key": "0017", "text_original": "有三年之練冠，則以大功之麻易之；唯杖屨不易。", "text_normalized": "有三年之練冠，則以大功之麻易之；唯杖屨不易。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 18, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 18", "sort_key": "0018", "text_original": "有父母之喪，尚功衰，而附兄弟之殤則練冠。附於殤，稱陽童某甫，不名，神也。", "text_normalized": "有父母之喪，尚功衰，而附兄弟之殤則練冠。附於殤，稱陽童某甫，不名，神也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 19, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 19", "sort_key": "0019", "text_original": "凡異居，始聞兄弟之喪，唯以哭對，可也。其始麻，散帶絰。未服麻而奔喪，及主人之未成絰也：疏者，與主人皆成之；親者，終其麻帶絰之日數。", "text_normalized": "凡異居，始聞兄弟之喪，唯以哭對，可也。其始麻，散帶絰。未服麻而奔喪，及主人之未成絰也：疏者，與主人皆成之；親者，終其麻帶絰之日數。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 20, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 20", "sort_key": "0020", "text_original": "主妾之喪，則自附至於練祥，皆使其子主之。其殯祭，不於正室。", "text_normalized": "主妾之喪，則自附至於練祥，皆使其子主之。其殯祭，不於正室。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 21, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 21", "sort_key": "0021", "text_original": "君不撫仆妾。", "text_normalized": "君不撫仆妾。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 22, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 22", "sort_key": "0022", "text_original": "女君死，則妾為女君之黨服。攝女君，則不為先女君之黨服。", "text_normalized": "女君死，則妾為女君之黨服。攝女君，則不為先女君之黨服。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 23, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 23", "sort_key": "0023", "text_original": "聞兄弟之喪，大功以上，見喪者之鄉而哭。適兄弟之送葬者弗及，遇主人於道，則遂之於墓。凡主兄弟之喪，雖疏亦虞之。", "text_normalized": "聞兄弟之喪，大功以上，見喪者之鄉而哭。適兄弟之送葬者弗及，遇主人於道，則遂之於墓。凡主兄弟之喪，雖疏亦虞之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 24, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 24", "sort_key": "0024", "text_original": "凡喪服未畢，有吊者，則為位而哭拜踴。", "text_normalized": "凡喪服未畢，有吊者，則為位而哭拜踴。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 25, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 25", "sort_key": "0025", "text_original": "大夫之哭大夫，弁絰；大夫與殯，亦弁絰。大夫有私喪之葛，則於其兄弟之輕喪，則弁絰。", "text_normalized": "大夫之哭大夫，弁絰；大夫與殯，亦弁絰。大夫有私喪之葛，則於其兄弟之輕喪，則弁絰。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0026", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 26, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 26", "sort_key": "0026", "text_original": "為長子杖，則其子不以杖即位。為妻，父母在，不杖，不稽顙。母在，不稽顙。稽顙者，其贈也拜。", "text_normalized": "為長子杖，則其子不以杖即位。為妻，父母在，不杖，不稽顙。母在，不稽顙。稽顙者，其贈也拜。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0027", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 27, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 27", "sort_key": "0027", "text_original": "違諸侯之大夫，不反服。違大夫之諸侯，不反服。", "text_normalized": "違諸侯之大夫，不反服。違大夫之諸侯，不反服。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0028", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 28, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 28", "sort_key": "0028", "text_original": "喪冠條屬，以別吉凶。三年之練冠，亦條屬，右縫。小功以下左。緦冠繰纓。大功以上散帶。", "text_normalized": "喪冠條屬，以別吉凶。三年之練冠，亦條屬，右縫。小功以下左。緦冠繰纓。大功以上散帶。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0029", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 29, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 29", "sort_key": "0029", "text_original": "朝服十五升，去其半而緦；加灰，錫也。", "text_normalized": "朝服十五升，去其半而緦；加灰，錫也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0030", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 30, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 30", "sort_key": "0030", "text_original": "諸侯相襚，以後路與冕服。先路與褒衣，不以襚。", "text_normalized": "諸侯相襚，以後路與冕服。先路與褒衣，不以襚。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0031", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 31, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 31", "sort_key": "0031", "text_original": "遣車視牢具。疏布輤，四面有章，置於四隅。載粻，有子曰：「非禮也。喪奠，脯醢而已。」", "text_normalized": "遣車視牢具。疏布輤，四面有章，置於四隅。載粻，有子曰：「非禮也。喪奠，脯醢而已。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0032", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 32, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 32", "sort_key": "0032", "text_original": "祭稱孝子、孝孫，喪稱哀子、哀孫。", "text_normalized": "祭稱孝子、孝孫，喪稱哀子、哀孫。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0033", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 33, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 33", "sort_key": "0033", "text_original": "端衰，喪車，皆無等。", "text_normalized": "端衰，喪車，皆無等。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0034", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 34, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 34", "sort_key": "0034", "text_original": "大白冠，緇布之冠，皆不蕤。委武玄縞而後蕤。", "text_normalized": "大白冠，緇布之冠，皆不蕤。委武玄縞而後蕤。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0035", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 35, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 35", "sort_key": "0035", "text_original": "大夫冕而祭於公，弁而祭於己。士弁而祭於公，冠而祭於己。士弁而親迎，然則士弁而祭於己可也。", "text_normalized": "大夫冕而祭於公，弁而祭於己。士弁而祭於公，冠而祭於己。士弁而親迎，然則士弁而祭於己可也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0036", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 36, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 36", "sort_key": "0036", "text_original": "暢臼以椈，杵以梧。枇以桑，長三尺；或曰五尺。畢用桑，長三尺，刊其柄與末。", "text_normalized": "暢臼以椈，杵以梧。枇以桑，長三尺；或曰五尺。畢用桑，長三尺，刊其柄與末。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0037", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 37, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 37", "sort_key": "0037", "text_original": "率帶，諸侯、大夫皆五采；士二采。", "text_normalized": "率帶，諸侯、大夫皆五采；士二采。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0038", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 38, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 38", "sort_key": "0038", "text_original": "醴者，稻醴也。甕甒筲衡，實見間而後折入。", "text_normalized": "醴者，稻醴也。甕甒筲衡，實見間而後折入。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0039", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 39, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 39", "sort_key": "0039", "text_original": "重，既虞而埋之。", "text_normalized": "重，既虞而埋之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0040", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 40, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 40", "sort_key": "0040", "text_original": "凡婦人，從其夫之爵位。", "text_normalized": "凡婦人，從其夫之爵位。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0041", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 41, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 41", "sort_key": "0041", "text_original": "小斂、大斂、啟，皆辯拜。", "text_normalized": "小斂、大斂、啟，皆辯拜。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0042", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 42, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 42", "sort_key": "0042", "text_original": "朝夕哭，不帷。無柩者不帷。", "text_normalized": "朝夕哭，不帷。無柩者不帷。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0043", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 43, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 43", "sort_key": "0043", "text_original": "君若載而後吊之，則主人東面而拜，門右北面而踴。出待，反而後奠。", "text_normalized": "君若載而後吊之，則主人東面而拜，門右北面而踴。出待，反而後奠。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0044", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 44, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 44", "sort_key": "0044", "text_original": "子羔之襲也：繭衣裳與稅衣纁袡為一，素端一，皮弁一，爵弁一，玄冕一。曾子曰：「不襲婦服。」", "text_normalized": "子羔之襲也：繭衣裳與稅衣纁袡為一，素端一，皮弁一，爵弁一，玄冕一。曾子曰：「不襲婦服。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0045", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 45, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 45", "sort_key": "0045", "text_original": "為君使而死，於公館，復；私館不復。公館者，公宮與公所為也。私館者，自卿大夫以下之家也。", "text_normalized": "為君使而死，於公館，復；私館不復。公館者，公宮與公所為也。私館者，自卿大夫以下之家也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0046", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 46, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 46", "sort_key": "0046", "text_original": "公七踴，大夫五踴，婦人居間，士三踴，婦人皆居間。", "text_normalized": "公七踴，大夫五踴，婦人居間，士三踴，婦人皆居間。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0047", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 47, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 47", "sort_key": "0047", "text_original": "公襲：卷衣一，玄端一，朝服一，素積一，纁裳一，爵弁二，玄冕一，褒衣一。朱綠帶，申加大帶於上。", "text_normalized": "公襲：卷衣一，玄端一，朝服一，素積一，纁裳一，爵弁二，玄冕一，褒衣一。朱綠帶，申加大帶於上。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0048", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 48, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 48", "sort_key": "0048", "text_original": "小斂環絰，公大夫士一也。", "text_normalized": "小斂環絰，公大夫士一也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0049", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 49, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 49", "sort_key": "0049", "text_original": "公視大斂，公升，商祝鋪席，乃斂。", "text_normalized": "公視大斂，公升，商祝鋪席，乃斂。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0050", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 50, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 50", "sort_key": "0050", "text_original": "魯人之贈也：三玄二纁，廣尺，長終幅。", "text_normalized": "魯人之贈也：三玄二纁，廣尺，長終幅。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0051", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 51, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 51", "sort_key": "0051", "text_original": "吊者即位於門西，東面；其介在其東南，北面西上，西於門。主孤西面。相者受命曰：「孤某使某請事。」客曰：「寡君使某，如何不淑！」相者入告，出曰：「孤某須矣。」吊者入，主人升堂，西面。吊者升自西階，東面，致命曰：「寡君聞君之喪，寡君使某，如何不淑！」子拜稽顙，吊者降，反位。", "text_normalized": "吊者即位於門西，東面；其介在其東南，北面西上，西於門。主孤西面。相者受命曰：「孤某使某請事。」客曰：「寡君使某，如何不淑！」相者入告，出曰：「孤某須矣。」吊者入，主人升堂，西面。吊者升自西階，東面，致命曰：「寡君聞君之喪，寡君使某，如何不淑！」子拜稽顙，吊者降，反位。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0052", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 52, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 52", "sort_key": "0052", "text_original": "含者執璧將命曰：「寡君使某含。」相者入告，出曰：「孤某須矣。」含者入，升堂，致命。再拜稽顙。含者坐委于殯東南，有葦席；既葬，蒲席。降，出，反位。宰朝服，即喪屨升自西階，西面，坐取璧，降自西階以東。", "text_normalized": "含者執璧將命曰：「寡君使某含。」相者入告，出曰：「孤某須矣。」含者入，升堂，致命。再拜稽顙。含者坐委于殯東南，有葦席；既葬，蒲席。降，出，反位。宰朝服，即喪屨升自西階，西面，坐取璧，降自西階以東。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0053", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 53, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 53", "sort_key": "0053", "text_original": "襚者曰：「寡君使某襚。」相者入告，出曰：「孤某須矣。」襚者執冕服；左執領，右執要，入，升堂致命曰：「寡君使某襚。」子拜稽顙。委衣於殯東。襚者降，受爵弁服於門內溜，將命，子拜稽顙，如初。受皮弁服於中庭。自西階受朝服，自堂受玄端，將命，子拜稽顙，皆如初。襚者降，出，反位。宰夫五人，舉以東。降自西階。其舉亦西面。", "text_normalized": "襚者曰：「寡君使某襚。」相者入告，出曰：「孤某須矣。」襚者執冕服；左執領，右執要，入，升堂致命曰：「寡君使某襚。」子拜稽顙。委衣於殯東。襚者降，受爵弁服於門內溜，將命，子拜稽顙，如初。受皮弁服於中庭。自西階受朝服，自堂受玄端，將命，子拜稽顙，皆如初。襚者降，出，反位。宰夫五人，舉以東。降自西階。其舉亦西面。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0054", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 54, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 54", "sort_key": "0054", "text_original": "上介賵：執圭將命，曰：「寡君使某賵。」相者入告，反命曰：「孤某須矣。」陳乘黃大路於中庭，北輈。執圭將命。客使自下，由路西。子拜稽顙，坐委於殯東南隅。宰舉以東。", "text_normalized": "上介賵：執圭將命，曰：「寡君使某賵。」相者入告，反命曰：「孤某須矣。」陳乘黃大路於中庭，北輈。執圭將命。客使自下，由路西。子拜稽顙，坐委於殯東南隅。宰舉以東。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0055", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 55, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 55", "sort_key": "0055", "text_original": "凡將命，鄉殯將命，子拜稽顙。西面而坐，委之。宰舉璧與圭，宰夫舉襚，升自西階，西面，坐取之，降自西階。賵者出，反位于門外。", "text_normalized": "凡將命，鄉殯將命，子拜稽顙。西面而坐，委之。宰舉璧與圭，宰夫舉襚，升自西階，西面，坐取之，降自西階。賵者出，反位于門外。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0056", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 56, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 56", "sort_key": "0056", "text_original": "上客臨曰：「寡君有宗廟之事，不得承事，使一介老某相執綍。」相者反命曰：「孤某須矣。」臨者入門右，介者皆從之，立於其左東上。宗人納賓，升，受命於君；降曰：「孤敢辭吾子之辱，請吾子之復位。」客對曰：「寡君命某，毋敢視賓客，敢辭。」宗人反命曰：「孤敢固辭吾子之辱，請吾子之復位。」客對曰：「寡君命某，毋敢視賓客，敢固辭。」宗人反命曰：「孤敢固辭吾子之辱，請吾子之復位。」客對曰：「寡君命使臣某，毋敢視賓客，是以敢固辭。固辭不獲命，敢不敬從。」", "text_normalized": "上客臨曰：「寡君有宗廟之事，不得承事，使一介老某相執綍。」相者反命曰：「孤某須矣。」臨者入門右，介者皆從之，立於其左東上。宗人納賓，升，受命於君；降曰：「孤敢辭吾子之辱，請吾子之復位。」客對曰：「寡君命某，毋敢視賓客，敢辭。」宗人反命曰：「孤敢固辭吾子之辱，請吾子之復位。」客對曰：「寡君命某，毋敢視賓客，敢固辭。」宗人反命曰：「孤敢固辭吾子之辱，請吾子之復位。」客對曰：「寡君命使臣某，毋敢視賓客，是以敢固辭。固辭不獲命，敢不敬從。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0057", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 57, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 57", "sort_key": "0057", "text_original": "客立於門西，介立於其左，東上。孤降自阼階，拜之，升哭，與客拾踴三。客出，送於門外，拜稽顙。", "text_normalized": "客立於門西，介立於其左，東上。孤降自阼階，拜之，升哭，與客拾踴三。客出，送於門外，拜稽顙。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0058", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 58, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 58", "sort_key": "0058", "text_original": "其國有君喪，不敢受吊。", "text_normalized": "其國有君喪，不敢受吊。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0059", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 59, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 59", "sort_key": "0059", "text_original": "外宗房中南面，小臣鋪席，商祝鋪絞紟衾，士盥於盤北。舉遷尸於斂上，卒斂，宰告子，馮之踴。夫人東面坐，馮之興踴。", "text_normalized": "外宗房中南面，小臣鋪席，商祝鋪絞紟衾，士盥於盤北。舉遷尸於斂上，卒斂，宰告子，馮之踴。夫人東面坐，馮之興踴。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0060", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i", "source_id": "liji-020-miscellaneous-records-i__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 60, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《雜記上》 60", "sort_key": "0060", "text_original": "士喪有與天子同者三：其終夜燎，及乘人，專道而行。", "text_normalized": "士喪有與天子同者三：其終夜燎，及乘人，專道而行。", "notes": ""}
